milestones.description: Wasim Akram has broken the record for most sixes (78) in ODIs for PAK, going past Saeed Anwar's 77
Shoaib Akhtar and Mohammad Yousuf's 92-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 81 between Saleem Malik and Aaqib Javed
This is the highest match aggregate (562) involving teams Australia & Pakistan in ODIs
